channel.title: Log In Error, Please help me?
channel.description: I run my server, then go into silab client and try to log on. For some reason, I can't get on, and neither did my friends. My server worked before, whats the problem? It happened the day after I downloaded, and used, D D S P 3 C V5. Please help me.

item.title: Log In Error, Please help me?
item.dc:creator: @Fireweaver0 Fireweaver0
item.description:
@Fireweaver0 wrote:

Learn a little more before you post…
Unless you messed up your server files or something THE ONLY REASON FOR THEM NOT BEING ABLE TO LOG IN IS A PORTFORWARD ERROR.

I can’t help you if you can’t help yourself.
The only other option i can think of is to system restore…
